data.description: This wonderful North East home has so much to offer. Oak trim and crown molding, updated kitchen, new kitchen appliances, furnace, hot water tank, patio for entertaining and 22X8 workshop off of the heated garage with 3rd garage door. Convenient 2nd Floor Laundry. The finished lower Level is a great place to entertain with family room and 1/2 bath.
